Mini-Aspire API

Mini-Aspire is a mini application that allows authenticated users to go through a loan application process and submit loan repayments. It provides a RESTful API for managing loans and repayments.

Installation
1. Enter the folder:
	cd mini-aspire-api
2. Create a virtual environment and activate it:
	python -m venv venv
	source venv/bin/activate
3. Install the dependencies:
	pip install -r requirements.txt


Usage
1. Start the development server:
	python Aspire_Mohit_Kuri.py
2. The API will be accessible at http://localhost:5000.


API Endpoints
	POST /loans: Create a loan
	PUT /loans/{loan_id}/approve: Approve a loan
	GET /loans/{loan_id}: Get loan details
	POST /loans/{loan_id}/repayments: Add a repayment to a loan


Unit Tests
	To run the unit tests, execute the following command:
		python -m unit_test.py discover tests